description: Experience elevated urban living in this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath corner unit at 33 Sleeper Street #409—a 2022 full gut renovation. Flooded with natural light from oversized windows on two exposures, this meticulously reimagined home blends historic charm with contemporary finishes. The open-concept layout features engineered hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and custom closets and shelving. Marble window sills throughout the unit add a seamless, refined touch. The designer kitchen includes Bosch appliances, sleek cabinetry, and a striking black quartz counter and backsplash. Spa-like bathrooms showcase floating vanities and a heated tile floor in the primary suite. Enjoy in-unit laundry and an 80-gallon hot water heater for year-round comfort. Located just steps from Seaport Boulevard, this home places you in the heart of Boston’s most vibrant neighborhood, near exceptional dining, shopping, nightlife, and the scenic harborfront.
